/OpenClaw-Pets-Widget\t\tpublic\t2026-03-25T09:42:46Z\nlxr1325/openclaw-pet\t基于飞书多维表格的虚拟小龙虾宠物系统\tpublic\t2026-03-13T07:05:14Z\nshufanli/openclaw-pet\t🦞 OpenClaw Molty 桌面萌宠 · Desktop Pet for OpenClaw users\tpublic\t2026-03-11T05:17:16Z\nlemonlyue/openclaw-pet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-22T15:29:26Z\nBlackBearCC/openclaw-pet\tOpenClaw Desktop Pet Assistant - 内嵌 OpenClaw AI 的桌面宠物助手\tpublic\t2026-03-21T13:03:02Z\n44-99/openclaw-desktop-pet\t🦞 A cute 3D desktop pet with real-time system monitoring and AI companionship\tpublic\t2026-03-23T08:26:02Z\niyuenan3/OpenClaw-PetsLog\t\tpublic\t2026-03-14T11:45:40Z\nPorfirio-Piero/openclaw-petresume\tModern resume portfolio built with Next.js, React, and Tailwind CSS\tpublic\t2026-03-03T11:35:19Z\nbigskytex05/openclaw_pet\tdigi pet for open claw\tpublic\t2026-03-17T03:10:45Z\npeterramsw/openclaw-peter\tClean Peter-maintained snapshot of openclaw v2026.3.8 plus GB10 carry patch\tpublic\t2026-03-14T04:49:16Z\njinyoung89/openclaw-pets\t\tpublic\t2026-02-21T16:26:23Z\nzhuoge-ouyang/openclaw_pet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-28T13:30:55Z\nsupermanhe/openclaw-lobster-pet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-07T17:03:49Z\nLeuIonOfficial/openclaw-pet-project\t\tpublic\t2026-03-26T22:18:42Z\nybgwon96/openclaw-desktop-pet\tOpenClaw 데스크톱 펫 - 공식 마스코트가 Dock 위를 걸어다니는 Tauri 2.0 앱\tpublic\t2026-02-22T17:43:43Z\nfloatj/openclaw_desktop_pet\tOpenClaw Desktop Pet\tpublic\t2026-03-24T15:13:28Z\nxiaotian283829691-dotcom/openclaw-desktop-pet\tOpenClaw 桌面宠物 — Live2D 猫团 + 像素风气泡 + AI 对话 🐱\tpublic\t2026-03-26T15:34:37Z\nT-X-R/OpenClawPixelPet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-16T02:14:04Z\n","name":"gh search"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774705037936}}
