alse,\"login\":\"rainnoon\",\"type\":\"User\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/rainnoon\"},\"stargazersCount\":9,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-27T10:22:15Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/rainnoon/oc-claw\"},{\"description\":\"🦞 A cute 3D desktop pet with real-time system monitoring and AI companionship\",\"name\":\"openclaw-desktop-pet\",\"owner\":{\"id\":\"U_kgDOCRAObA\",\"is_bot\":false,\"login\":\"44-99\",\"type\":\"User\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/44-99\"},\"stargazersCount\":5,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-23T08:26:02Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/44-99/openclaw-desktop-pet\"},{\"description\":\"OpenClaw skills that connect a physical ESP32 Tamagotchi (LCD + buttons) to a memecoin on nad.fun (Monad). Buy $MONA → pet gets fed. Sell → pet gets sad. Includes ESP32 firmware, blockchain event watcher, and AI agent skills that bridge on-chain trades to real-time pet reactions.\",\"name\":\"monagotchi\",\"owner\":{\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjI0Nzc4NTYw\",\"is_bot\":false,\"login\":\"This-Is-Captain-Code\",\"type\":\"User\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/This-Is-Captain-Code\"},\"stargazersCount\":14,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-10T15:02:21Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/This-Is-Captain-Code/monagotchi\"},{\"description\":\"OpenClaw Desktop Pet\",\"name\":\"openclaw_desktop_pet\",\"owner\":{\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjQyMTg5Mzg=\",\"is_bot\":false,\"login\":\"floatj\",\"type\":\"User\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/floatj\"},\"stargazersCount\":0,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-24T15:13:28Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/floatj/openclaw_desktop_pet\"},{\"description\":\"clado's openclaw pet :)\",\"name\":\"haku\",\"owner\":{\"id\":\"U_kgDOCyOWiQ\",\"is_bot\":false,\"login\":\"tomzhengy\",\"type\":\"User\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/tomzhengy\"},\"stargazersCount\":0,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-02T07:02:19Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/tomzhengy/haku\"}]\n","truncated":false,"exitCode":0},{"sessionId":"tide-shore","status":"failed","startedAt":1774704986616,"endedAt":1774705006626,"runtimeMs":20010,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","command":"gh search repos 'openclaw-pet in:name' --limit 20 --json name,owner,description,url,updatedAt,stargazersCount","name":"gh search","tail":"","truncated":false,"exitSignal":"SIGTERM"},{"sessionId":"tidal-pine","status":"completed","startedAt":1774705032381,"endedAt":1774705033799,"runtimeMs":1418,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","command":"gh search repos 'openclaw-pet in:name' --limit 20","name":"gh search","tail":"leosssvip-dot/OpenClaw-Pets-Widget\t\tpublic\t2026-03-25T09:42:46Z\nlxr1325/openclaw-pet\t基于飞书多维表格的虚拟小龙虾宠物系统\tpublic\t2026-03-13T07:05:14Z\nshufanli/openclaw-pet\t🦞 OpenClaw Molty 桌面萌宠 · Desktop Pet for OpenClaw users\tpublic\t2026-03-11T05:17:16Z\nlemonlyue/openclaw-pet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-22T15:29:26Z\nBlackBearCC/openclaw-pet\tOpenClaw Desktop Pet Assistant - 内嵌 OpenClaw AI 的桌面宠物助手\tpublic\t2026-03-21T13:03:02Z\n44-99/openclaw-desktop-pet\t🦞 A cute 3D desktop pet with real-time system monitoring and AI companionship\tpublic\t2026-03-23T08:26:02Z\niyuenan3/OpenClaw-PetsLog\t\tpublic\t2026-03-14T11:45:40Z\nPorfirio-Piero/openclaw-petresume\tModern resume portfolio built with Next.js, React, and Tailwind CSS\tpublic\t2026-03-03T11:35:19Z\nbigskytex05/openclaw_pet\tdigi pet for open claw\tpublic\t2026-03-17T03:10:45Z\npeterramsw/openclaw-peter\tClean Peter-maintained snapshot of openclaw v2026.3.8 plus GB10 carry patch\tpublic\t2026-03-14T04:49:16Z\njinyoung89/openclaw-pets\t\tpublic\t2026-02-21T16:26:23Z\nzhuoge-ouyang/openclaw_pet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-28T13:30:55Z\nsupermanhe/openclaw-lobster-pet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-07T17:03:49Z\nLeuIonOfficial/openclaw-pet-project\t\tpublic\t2026-03-26T22:18:42Z\nybgwon96/openclaw-desktop-pet\tOpenClaw 데스크톱 펫 - 공식 마스코트가 Dock 위를 걸어다니는 Tauri 2.0 앱\tpublic\t2026-02-22T17:43:43Z\nfloatj/openclaw_desktop_pet\tOpenClaw Desktop Pet\tpublic\t2026-03-24T15:13:28Z\nxiaotian283829691-dotcom/openclaw-desktop-pet\tOpenClaw 桌面宠物 — Live2D 猫团 + 像素风气泡 + AI 对话 🐱\tpublic\t2026-03-26T15:34:37Z\nT-X-R/OpenClawPixelPet\t\tpublic\t2026-03-16T02:14:04Z\n","truncated":false,"exitCode":0},{"sessionId":"fresh-nexus","status":"completed","startedAt":1774705032380,"endedAt":1774705034092,"runtimeMs":1712,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","command":"gh api repos/rainnoon/oc-claw/readme -H 'Accept: application/vnd.github.raw+json'","name":"gh api","tail":"ackgrounds with crop tool\n- Completion & waiting sound effects\n- Menu bar only — no dock icon\n\n## Requirements\n\n- macOS (MacBook with notch recommended)\n- [OpenClaw](https://github.com/nicepkg/openclaw) and/or [Claude Code](https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code) installed\n\n## Install\n\n> [!TIP]\n> **Tell your AI agent (OpenClaw / Claude Code):**\n>\n> ```\n> Install oc-claw: curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rainnoon/oc-claw/main/install.sh | bash\n> ```\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> **Or run it yourself in Terminal:**\n>\n> ```bash\n> curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rainnoon/oc-claw/main/install.sh | bash\n> ```\n>\n> You can also download the DMG from [Releases](https://github.com/rainnoon/oc-claw/releases). After installing, run `xattr -cr /Applications/oc-claw.app` to bypass macOS Gatekeeper.\n\n## How it works\n\n```\nOpenClaw Agents ──→ JSONL session files ──→ Health polling ──→ Activity state\nClaude Code     ──→ Hooks (SessionStart/Stop) ──→ Event parser ──→ Activity state\n                                                                        ↓\n                                        Animated sprites ← State machine ← Sound effects\n```\n\nOC-Claw polls OpenClaw session files to detect agent activity, and listens to Claude Code via installed hooks. Activity states drive character animations on the notch island, with an expandable panel for session details, chat history, and metrics.\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- **Tauri v2** + **React** + **TypeScript** — frontend\n- **Rust** — backend for system interaction, SSH tunneling, and API communication\n- macOS native APIs for notch positioning and window management\n\n## Development\n\n```bash\ncd frontend\nnpm install\nnpx tauri dev\n```\n\n## Contributing\n\nBug reports, feature suggestions, and pull requests are welcome.\n\n## Credits\n\n- [Notchi](https://github.com/sk-ruban/notchi) — design inspiration for notch companion concept and grass island\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <sub>Originally created at KAON Hackathon</sub>\n</p>\n","truncated":false,"exitCode":0},{"sessionId":"marine-shell","status":"failed","startedAt":1774705032381,"endedAt":1774705052390,"runtimeMs":20009,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","command":"gh api repos/44-99/openclaw-desktop-pet/readme -H 'Accept: application/vnd.github.raw+json'","name":"gh api","tail":"","truncated":false,"exitSignal":"SIGTERM"},{"sessionId":"mild-willow","status":"completed","startedAt":1774705073387,"endedAt":1774705074888,"runtimeMs":1501,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","command":"gh api repos/BlackBearCC/openclaw-pet/readme -H 'Accept: application/vnd.github.raw+json' | sed -n '1,220p'","name":"gh api","tail":" 主进程、窗口 620×580、IPC 路由\n│   ├── preload.js             安全桥接 window.electronAPI\n│   ├── llm-service.js         Gateway 管理 + 流式对话 + Agent 事件\n│   └── win32-monitor.js       Win32 前台窗口轮询\n├── src/\n│   ├── app.js                 渲染入口，串联所有子系统\n│   ├── pet/\n│   │   ├── PetRenderer.js     Canvas 动画渲染器 (960px)\n│   │   ├── SpriteSheet.js     Spritesheet 加载 + 帧绘制\n│   │   ├── StateMachine.js    18 种动画状态机\n│   │   ├── Behaviors.js       自主行为调度 + 边缘检测\n│   │   ├── MoodSystem.js      心情系统（衰减 + 离线补算）\n│   │   ├── HungerSystem.js    饱腹度系统\n│   │   ├── HealthSystem.js    健康值系统（饱腹+心情联合驱动）\n│   │   ├── IntimacySystem.js  亲密度 / 4 阶段成长\n│   │   ├── FeedingAnimator.js 4 阶段喂食动画\n│   │   ├── DomainSystem.js    7 领域 + 5 属性 + 权重矩阵（静态定义）\n│   │   ├── SkillSystem.js     领域活跃度 + 领悟触发 + 属性 XP 成长（原 KnowledgeSystem + SkillUnlockSystem 合并）\n│   │   ├── PetAI.js           宠物内心独白 LLM 直连\n│   │   ├── AchievementSystem.js 12 枚成就徽章\n│   │   ├── MiniCatSystem.js   子代理迷你猫伴侣 (≤4)\n│   │   ├── AgentStatsTracker.js 子会话工具统计\n│   │   └── WorkspaceWatcher.js  前台窗口标题解析\n│   ├── interaction/\n│   │   ├── DragHandler.js     窗口拖拽\n│   │   ├── ClickHandler.js    单击/双击/长按 (1.5s)\n│   │   ├── FileDropHandler.js 文件拖放分析 (35 种格式)\n│   │   └── ContextMenu.js     右键菜单 + 状态条\n│   ├── ui/\n│   │   ├── ChatPanel.js       聊天面板（流式 + 多会话）\n│   │   ├── StreamingBubble.js 堆叠消息气泡 (≤8 段)\n│   │   ├── MarkdownPanel.js   Markdown 渲染面板\n│   │   ├── BottomChatInput.js 底部浮动快捷输入\n│   │   ├── SettingsPanel.js   设置面板\n│   │   ├── SkillPanel.js      四页图鉴（工具/技能+属性/代理/成就）\n│   │   ├── ToolStatusBar.js   工具执行状态栏\n│   │   └── AgentConnections.js SVG 连线可视化\n│   ├── bridge/\n│   │   └── OpenClawBridge.js  (已弃用)\n│   └── utils/\n│       └── textSplitter.js    标点分句工具\n├── assets/sprites/            帧动画资源 (19 张 spritesheet)\n└── scripts/                   工具脚本\n```\n\n## 替换动画资源\n\n1. 准备 128×128 的序列帧 PNG\n2. 打包成 spritesheet（如 TexturePacker）\n3. 生成 JSON 元数据（参考 `assets/sprites/placeholder/spritesheet.json`）\n4. 放到 `assets/sprites/` 对应目录\n5. 复合动画需额外准备 enter/loop/exit 三张 spritesheet\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n","truncated":false,"exitCode":0},{"sessionId":"plaid-lagoon","status":"completed","startedAt":1774705073387,"endedAt":1774705075269,"runtimeMs":1882,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","command":"gh repo view BlackBearCC/openclaw-pet --json name,description,url,primaryLanguage,updatedAt,stargazerCount,defaultBranchRef","name":"gh repo","tail":"{\"defaultBranchRef\":{\"name\":\"main\"},\"description\":\"OpenClaw Desktop Pet Assistant - 内嵌 OpenClaw AI 的桌面宠物助手\",\"name\":\"openclaw-pet\",\"primaryLanguage\":{\"name\":\"JavaScript\"},\"stargazerCount\":1,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-21T13:03:02Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/BlackBearCC/openclaw-pet\"}\n","truncated":false,"exitCode":0},{"sessionId":"crisp-glade","status":"completed","startedAt":1774705073387,"endedAt":1774705075310,"runtimeMs":1923,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","command"